{"id":243244,"type":2,"name":"Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Mouse","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/58/1e/243244_aw4PE.jpg","rating":{"total":14,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":1,"7":8,"8":4,"9":0,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"　　清晨，送奶工将一瓶新鲜的牛奶放到了门口。馋嘴的汤姆趁主人不注意，偷偷将牛奶收入自己的囊中。正当他打算好好享用盘中的牛奶时，却发现小老鼠杰瑞丝毫不见外地来到盘子边大快朵颐。小气的汤姆自然不会允许杰瑞分享自己的美食，他三番五次想敢走这个讨厌的小家伙，但是杰瑞似乎打定了主意，非要分得一杯羹不可。汤姆气急败坏，躲进实验室用各种强酸调配了剧毒的牛奶，之后将其放在了杰瑞的洞口。 \r\n　　杰瑞不知是计，大口大口喝下牛奶，结果痛苦地倒在了洞口。汤姆还未来得及高兴，竟发现杰瑞瞬间变成了体形庞大、力量过人的怪物。笨蛋汤姆这回自食其果……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>强力乳液</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/1925\">Robert Louis Stevenson</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1947-06-14</li><li><span>片长: </span>7分09秒</li><li><span>类型: </span>喜剧 / 动画 / 短片 / 家庭</li><li><span>导演: </span>Joseph Barbera、William Hanna</li><li><span>IMDb链接: </span>tt0039338</li>","collection":{"collect":21,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"1947","count":3},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":3},{"name":"欧美","count":2},{"name":"短片","count":2},{"name":"美国","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":912258,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/912258","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":1925,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/09/50/1925_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"罗伯特·路易斯·史蒂文森","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":132373,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/08/21/132373_AjqtP.jpg","title":"The Cat Concerto","type":"前传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/132373"},{"id":263189,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/32/1e/263189_2rhi0.jpg","title":"Salt Water Tabby","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/263189"},{"id":25961,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/fd/60/25961_WDKz6.jpg","title":"Tom and Jerry","type":"不同演绎","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/25961"},{"id":277144,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/fd/a7/277144_Sj5u0.jpg","title":"Strange Case of Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/277144"}]}